#a simple mapping for holding the wiimote horizontally
#Great for classic games using a dpad and two action buttons.


assign wiimote up left
assign wiimote left down
assign wiimote right up
assign wiimote down right
assign wiimote a north
assign wiimote b west
assign wiimote 1 south
assign wiimote 2 east
assign wiimote plus start
assign wiimote home mode
assign wiimote minus select


#Tilt controls are mapped to a virtual left-stick,
#but the accelerometers are off by default.

disable wiimote accel
assign wiimote accelx left_y invert
assign wiimote accely left_x invert

#The IR sensor is just going to be pointing at a hand.
#No need to enable it.
disable wiimote IR
